How to ask in French

1) Please !
  In French you can use "s'il vous plait" or "s'il te plait" depend on who are you talking to (check variation-of-subject)
  *Example : Oui,s'il vous plait !
2) Want 
  In French you can use "veux","veut",and "voulons" 
  *Example : Je veux une pomme
3) Would like 
  In French you can use "voudrais"
  *Example : Je voudrais un croissant
